text: ( Source : US Department of Defense ) ABOARD A MILITARY AIRCRAFT, October 20 , 2015 - The chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff today detailed the campaign against the Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant following a visit to Iraq . Marine Corps
